QuestData.Title: Equipping Our Fleet
QuestData.Description: Commander, our fleet is going to require some custom naval equipment if we hope to stand a chance in this war. Find Kronk Rustspark down at the docks, he should be able to help us out.
QuestData.PortraitGiverText: Find Kronk Rustspark at the dry docks.
QuestData.LogDescription: Meet Kronk Rustspark at the docks.

Objectives.Objective: Find Kronk Rustspark on the docks
